"> <div id="zone_1355" data-zone-id="1355" class="no-init" data-zone-viewtype="banner" data-google-query-id="CNnNiK-dmJIDFSvQRAcdFhkv7w" style=""><div id="google_ads_iframe_/31903365/Haberturk//Gundem//160x600//Sol_0__container__" style="border: 0pt none; display: inline-block; width: 160px; height: 600px;"><iframe frameborder="0" src="./erd_files/container.html" id="google_ads_iframe_/31903365/Haberturk//Gundem//160x600//Sol_0" title="Üçüncü taraf reklam içeriği" name="" scrolling="no" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" width="160" height="600" data-is-safeframe="true" sandbox="allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation" allow="private-state-token-redemption;attribution-reporting" aria-label="Reklam" tabindex="0" data-google-container-id="5" style="border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom;" data-load-complete="true"></iframe></div></div> </div> <script> function renderPageSkinLeft() { if (!window.rightAdsIsPageskin) { cbgAds.RefreshZone(1355); } } </script>         <div class="w-full min-w-full">         <div class="masthead-top w-full min-h-[250px] flex mb-5 justify-center items-center bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 overflow-hidden"> <div class="wrapper w-[970px] flex items-center justify-center"> <div id="zone_1289" class="ads-zone flex items-center justify-center refreshed-zone"> <div id="zone_1289_mhc" data-zone-viewtype="banner" data-zone-id="1289" class="flex items-center justify-center" style="min-height: 250px; display: none;" data-google-query-id="CPvC4K6dmJIDFQpZkQQdSbUFWw"><div id="google_ads_iframe_/31903365/Haberturk//Gundem//Masthead_0__container__" style="border: 0pt none; width: 970px; height: 0px;"></div></div> </div> <script> cbgAds.AdsInline(1289); </script> </div> </div>              <div class="news-wrapper it-container w-full flex flex-wrap">  <article class="news-tracker it-main it-item w-[calc(100%-300px)] pr-7 news-items" data-id="3854645" data-it="{&quot;index&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:3854645,&quot;next&quot;:&quot;\/infinite\/news\/3854642&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Cumhurba\u015fkan\u0131 Recep Tayyip Erdo\u011fan: Ter\u00f6r d\u00f6nemi tamamen kapanm\u0131\u015ft\u0131r&quot;,&quot;tracker&quot;:[{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;history&quot;,&quot;parameter&quot;:&quot;full&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;\/cumhurbaskani-recep-tayyip-erdogan-teror-donemi-tamamen-kapanmistir-3854645&quot;}]}" property="articleBody"> <div class="widget-breadcrumb mb-4 py-1 overflow-hidden border-b dark:border-gray-800 flex justify-between "> <div class="block text-xs text-gray-500">  <span>  <a href="https://www.haberturk.com/">Haberler</a> <i class="ht-icon-chevron-right inline-block mx-1 w-1 h-1 text-xxxs text-black dark:text-white"></i>  </span>  <span>  <a href="https://www.haberturk.com/gundem">Gündem</a> <i class="ht-icon-chevron-right inline-block mx-1 w-1 h-1 text-xxxs text-black dark:text-white"></i>  </span>  <span>  <span class="font-bold">Cumhurbaşkanı Recep Tayyip Erdoğan: Terör dönemi tamamen kapanmıştır</span>  </span>  </div> </div>             <div class="featured"> <div class="pl-5 aspect-h-1">  <h1 class="text-3xl font-black mb-4">Cumhurbaşkanı Recep Tayyip Erdoğan: Terör dönemi tamamen kapanmıştır</h1> <h2 class="text-base mb-4 text-red-600 dark:text-inherit">Kabine toplantısı sonrası konuşan Cumhurbaşkanı Erdoğan, "Suriye ile çok yakından ilgileniyoruz" diyerek bölgedeki barış ve entegrasyon sürecine destek verdi; "Bölgemizde terörün devri tamamen kapanmıştır" mesajıyla birlik ve huzur vurgusu yaptı ve Atlas yavrumuzu katledenlerin hukuk önünde en ağır cezayı alması için sürecin sıkı takipçisi olacaklarını açıkladı.</h2> </div>      <div class="relative flex justify-between items-center mb-5 py-3 border-t border-b border-dashed dark:border-gray-800"> <div class="flex mr-5">   <div class="widget-info flex items-center">  <div class="overflow-hidden w-7 h-7 rounded-full mr-3 p-1 flex justify-center items-center bg-gray-100 aspect-w-1 aspect-h-1">      <img width="28" height="28" src="./erd_files/haberturk.svg" data-big-src="" alt="Kaynak" class=" w-full rounded-full b-loaded">         </div>  <div class="flex flex-col"> <span class="text-xs">Habertürk</span> </div> <div class="w-px h-7 mx-5 border-r border-dashed dark:border-gray-800"></div> </div>   <div class="h-10 flex flex-col justify-center text-xs"> <span> <b>Giriş: </b> 19.01.2026 - 18:43 </span> <span> <b>Güncelleme: </b> 19.01.2026 - 19:37 </span> </div>  </div> <div class="relative"> <ul class="widget-share flex justify-end w-full overflow-x-auto text-center text-gray-500">  <li class="m-1 dark:bg-gray-800 ml-0">  <a href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.haberturk.com%2Fcumhurbaskani-recep-tayyip-erdogan-teror-donemi-tamamen-kapanmistir-3854645%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Darticleshare%26utm_campaign%3Dwebsite" target="_blank" title="facebookda paylaş" class="facebook flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 border dark:border-gray-800"> <i style="color:#0264d3" class="ht-icon-facebook dark:!text-white text-sm"></i> </a> <span class="text-xxs hidden">facebook</span> </li>  <li class="m-1 dark:bg-gray-800 ">  <a href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=Cumhurba%C5%9Fkan%C4%B1%20Erdo%C4%9Fan%27dan%20a%C3%A7%C4%B1klamalar&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.haberturk.com%2Fcumhurbaskani-recep-tayyip-erdogan-teror-donemi-tamamen-kapanmistir-3854645%3Futm_source%3Dtwitter%26utm_medium%3Darticleshare%26utm_campaign%3Dwebsite&amp;original_referer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.haberturk.com%2Fcumhurbaskani-recep-tayyip-erdogan-teror-donemi-tamamen-kapanmistir-3854645%3Futm_source%3Dtwitter%26utm_medium%3Darticleshare%26utm_campaign%3Dwebsite&amp;via=haberturk" target="_blank" title="twitter-xda paylaş" class="twitter-x flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 border dark:border-gray-800"> <i style="color:#0f1419" class="ht-icon-twitter-x dark:!text-white text-sm"></i> </a> <span class="text-xxs hidden">twitter-x</span> 