t\u0131r\u0131ld\u0131. Gen\u00e7'in tutukluluk halinin devam\u0131na karar verildi. Eski \u015ei\u015fli Belediye Ba\u015fkan\u0131 Hayri \u0130n\u00f6n\u00fc ve eski Maltepe Belediye Ba\u015fkan yard\u0131mc\u0131s\u0131 Melih Mors\u00fcnb\u00fcl 6 y\u0131l 3 ay hapis cezas\u0131na \u00e7arpt\u0131r\u0131l\u0131rken, Mustaf Sar\u0131g\u00fcl'\u00fcn o\u011flu Emir Sar\u0131g\u00fcl 2 y\u0131l 1 ay hapis cezas\u0131na \u00e7arpt\u0131r\u0131ld\u0131. Habert\u00fcrk'ten Ceylan Sever'in haberi..","slug":"belediyelere-yonelik-dhkpc-davasinda-sukru-genc-e-7-yil-hapis-karari","writer":"1836","category":{"type":"category","items":[{"id":110,"name":"G\u00fcndem","url":"\/gundem","appUrl":"cbg:\/\/haber\/kategori\/ht\/gundem"},{"id":4061544,"name":"G\u00fcncel","url":"\/gundem\/guncel","appUrl":"cbg:\/\/haber\/kategori\/ht\/gundem\/guncel"}]},"url":"\/belediyelere-yonelik-dhkpc-davasinda-sukru-genc-e-7-yil-hapis-karari-3854585","appUrl":"cbg:\/\/haber\/detay\/3854585","ampUrl":"\/belediyelere-yonelik-dhkpc-davasinda-sukru-genc-e-7-yil-hapis-karari-3854585-amp","newsMetaData":{"textColor":"text-white","appTextColor":"white","newsDetailType":"type1","headline":"","emoji":0,"specialColor":"","specialColorText":""},"fastLinkText":"Eski Sar\u0131yer Belediye Ba\u015fkan\u0131 \u015e\u00fckr\u00fc Gen\u00e7'e 7,5 y\u0131l ceza verildi","updatedDateTime":"2026-01-19 16:02:16","updatedDateTimeFormatted":"3 dakika \u00f6nce","urlTarget":"_blank","updatedElapsedTimeFormatted":"1 saat \u00f6nce","image":{"imageUrlBase":"https:\/\/im.haberturk.com\/l\/2026\/01\/19\/ver1768827756\/3854585\/jpg\/","imageUrlHeadlineDesktop":"","imageUrlHeadlineMobile":"","showHeadlineTitle":true,"title":"","ratio":{"width":1,"height":1}},"lastMinuteNews":false,"gtmTracker":{"class":"gtm-tracker","dataAttr":"data-newslist=\"sidebar\" data-newsposition=\"7\" data-newsid=\"3854585\" data-newsname=\"\u015e\u00fckr\u00fc Gen\u00e7'e 7 y\u0131l hapis cezas\u0131\" data-newsvariant=\"news\" data-newscategory=\"G\u00fcndem\""}},{"newsId":3854559,"type":"news","title":"Karde\u015f cinayetinde caninin ifadesi ortaya \u00e7\u0131kt\u0131!","spot":"Antalya'da a\u011fabeyi Vedat Ulu\u011ftekin'i \u00f6ld\u00fcr\u00fcp, di\u011fer a\u011fabeyinin e\u015fi Z. Ulu\u011ftekin'i yaralayan Mehmet Emin Ulu\u011ftekin ile birlikte 6 \u015f\u00fcpheli daha g\u00f6zalt\u0131na al\u0131nd\u0131. Cinayeti itiraf eden zanl\u0131n\u0131n ilk ifadesinde, \"Namus meselesinden dolay\u0131 i\u015fledim. Abim ve di\u011fer abimin e\u015fi aras\u0131nda ili\u015fki oldu\u011funu \u00f6\u011frendim. Kendime yediremedim, olay\u0131 ger\u00e7ekle\u015ftirmeye karar verip, cinayeti i\u015fledim\" dedi\u011fi \u00f6\u011frenildi.","slug":"kardes-cinayetinde-caninin-ifadesi-ortaya-cikti-namus-iddiasi","writer":"","category":{"type":"category","items":[{"id":110,"name":"G\u00fcndem","url":"\/gundem","appUrl":"cbg:\/\/haber\/kategori\/ht\/gundem"},{"id":4060590,"name":"3. Sayfa","url":"\/gundem\/ucuncu-sayfa","appUrl":"cbg:\/\/haber\/kategori\/ht\/gundem\/ucuncu-sayfa"}]},"url":"\/kardes-cinayetinde-caninin-ifadesi-ortaya-cikti-namus-iddiasi-3854559","appUrl":"cbg:\/\/haber\/detay\/3854559","ampUrl":"\/kardes-cinayetinde-caninin-ifadesi-ortaya-cikti-namus-iddiasi-3854559-amp","newsMetaData":{"textColor":"text-white","appTextColor":"white","newsDetailType":"type1","headline":"","emoji":0,"specialColor":"","specialColorText":""},"fastLinkText":"Karde\u015f cinayetinde caninin ifadesi ortaya \u00e7\u0131kt\u0131! Namus iddias\u0131!","updatedDateTime":"2026-01-19 15:58:47","updatedDateTimeFormatted":"1 saat \u00f6nce","urlTarget":"_blank","updatedElapsedTimeFormatted":"4 saat \u00f6nce","image":{"imageUrlBase":"https:\/\/im.haberturk.com\/l\/2026\/01\/19\/ver1768827551\/3854559\/jpg\/","imageUrlHeadlineDesktop":"https:\/\/im.haberturk.com\/l\/2026\/01\/19\/ver1768827551\/3854559_manset\/jpg\/640x640","imageUrlHeadlineMobile":"https:\/\/im.haberturk.com\/l\/2026\/01\/19\/ver1768827551\/3854559_manset\/jpg\/414x414","showHeadlineTitle":false,"title":"","ratio":{"width":1,"height":1}},"lastMinuteNews":false,"gtmTracker":{"class":"gtm-tracker","dataAttr":"data-newslist=\"sidebar\" data-newsposition=\"8\" data-newsid=\"3854559\" data-newsname=\"Karde\u015f cinayetinde caninin ifadesi ortaya \u00e7\u0131kt\u0131!\" data-newsvariant=\"news\" data-newscategory=\"G\u00fcndem\""}},{"newsId":3854452,"type":"news","title":"Kuryeler dikkat! \u0130stanbul Valili\u011fi saati a\u00e7\u0131klad\u0131! Trafik yasa\u011f\u0131 s\u00fcrecek!","spot":"\u0130stanbul trafi\u011finde kar ya\u011f\u0131\u015f\u0131 \u00f6nlemi! \u0130stanbul Valili\u011fi'nce, saat: 10.00'dan itibaren kurye ve a\u011f\u0131r ta\u015f\u0131tlar\u0131n trafi\u011fe \u00e7\u0131k\u0131\u015f\u0131 yasakland\u0131. Kamyonlar\u0131n trafi\u011fe \u00e7\u0131k\u0131\u015f yasa\u011f\u0131n\u0131n saat: 16.00'da sona erece\u011fi, kuryelerin ise yar\u0131n sabah saat: 10.00'a kadar trafi\u011fe \u00e7\u0131kamayaca\u011f\u0131 bildirildi. Valilik, kentte ya\u011fmur ve karla kar\u0131\u015f\u0131k ya\u011fmurun devam edece\u011fini belirterek, buzlanma ve don olaylar\u0131na kar\u015f\u0131 dikkatli olunmas\u0131 uyar\u0131s\u0131nda bulundu. Sakarya ve Elaz\u0131\u011f'da da g\u00fcn boyu olumsuz hava ko\u015fullar\u0131 nedeniyle motokuryelerin trafi\u011fe \u00e7\u0131k\u0131\u015f\u0131n\u0131n durduruldu\u011fu bildirildi","slug":"istanbul-da-kurye-ve-agir-tasitlara-kar-yasagi","writer":"","category":{"type":"category","items":[{"id":110,"name":"G\u00fcndem","url":"\/gundem","appUrl":"cbg:\/\/haber\/kategori\/ht\/gundem"},{"id":4060603,"name":"Trafik","url":"\/gundem\/trafik","appUrl":"cbg:\/\/haber\/kategori\/ht\/gundem\/trafik"}]},"url":"\/istanbul-da-kurye-ve-agir-tasitlara-kar-yasagi-3854452","appUrl":"cbg:\/\/haber\/detay\/3854452","ampUrl":"\/istanbul-da-kurye-ve-agir-tasitlara-kar-yasagi-3854452-amp","newsMetaData":{"textColor":"text-white","appTextColor":"white","newsDetailType":"type1","headline":"","e