me' su\u00e7lar\u0131ndan tutukland\u0131. Fatih \u0130nan'\u0131n karde\u015fi \u00d6.\u0130.'nin, amcas\u0131 K.\u0130. ile mesajla\u015ft\u0131\u011f\u0131 tespit edildi. Amca K.\u0130.'nin, \"Eskisinden korkmuyorum, bundan korkuyorum\" mesaj\u0131na \u00d6.\u0130.'nin, \"Ses etmeyin\" diye yan\u0131t verdi\u011fi, \u00d6.\u0130.'nin ifadesinde s\u00f6z konusu mesajlar\u0131n Sar\u0131g\u00fcl'\u00fcn \u00f6l\u00fcm\u00fcyle ilgili oldu\u011funu s\u00f6yledi\u011fi \u00f6\u011frenildi","slug":"mihriban-yilmaz-in-katili-naile-busra-nin-olumunden-tutuklandi-bunun-adi-cifte-vahset-son-dakika-haber","writer":"","category":{"type":"category","items":[{"id":110,"name":"G\u00fcndem","url":"\/gundem","appUrl":"cbg:\/\/haber\/kategori\/ht\/gundem"},{"id":4060590,"name":"3. Sayfa","url":"\/gundem\/ucuncu-sayfa","appUrl":"cbg:\/\/haber\/kategori\/ht\/gundem\/ucuncu-sayfa"}]},"url":"\/mihriban-yilmaz-in-katili-naile-busra-nin-olumunden-tutuklandi-bunun-adi-cifte-vahset-son-dakika-haber-3854551","appUrl":"cbg:\/\/haber\/detay\/3854551","ampUrl":"\/mihriban-yilmaz-in-katili-naile-busra-nin-olumunden-tutuklandi-bunun-adi-cifte-vahset-son-dakika-haber-3854551-amp","newsMetaData":{"textColor":"text-white","appTextColor":"white","newsDetailType":"type1","headline":"","emoji":0,"specialColor":"","specialColorText":""},"fastLinkText":"Mihriban'\u0131n katili B\u00fc\u015fra'n\u0131n \u00f6l\u00fcm\u00fcnden tutukland\u0131! Bir mesajla ortaya \u00e7\u0131kan 2 kad\u0131n cinayeti!","updatedDateTime":"2026-01-19 15:08:42","updatedDateTimeFormatted":"2 saat \u00f6nce","urlTarget":"_blank","updatedElapsedTimeFormatted":"4 saat \u00f6nce","image":{"imageUrlBase":"https:\/\/im.haberturk.com\/l\/2026\/01\/19\/ver1768818625\/3854551\/jpg\/","imageUrlHeadlineDesktop":"https:\/\/im.haberturk.com\/l\/2026\/01\/19\/ver1768818625\/3854551_manset\/jpg\/640x640","imageUrlHeadlineMobile":"https:\/\/im.haberturk.com\/l\/2026\/01\/19\/ver1768818625\/3854551_manset\/jpg\/414x414","showHeadlineTitle":